| --- | --- | --- |
| **Scenario Prompt** | Text | User input or reflex trigger (e.g., â€œMy motion was deniedâ€) |
| **Detected Reflex** | Select | JC-Denial, JC-Silence, JC-Default, LCa-Misalignment, etc. |
